### ==========================================
### VARIANT — CREATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Create variant (admin — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON NEGRO 32",
    "stock": 10,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": {{productId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create variant 2 (editor — válido ✅ 201)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON BEIGE 32",
    "stock": 10,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": {{productId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create variant (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON NEGRO 32",
    "stock": 10,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": {{productId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create variant (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON NEGRO 32",
    "stock": 10,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": {{productId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Create variant (product_id no existe — 404 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON NEGRO 32",
    "stock": 10,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": 999
}

### ==========================================

### Create variant (stock negativo — 422 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/ HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "PANTALON NEGRO 32",
    "stock": -1,
    "cost": 59.90,
    "product_id": {{productId}}
}


### ==========================================
### VARIANT — SPEC VALUES (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Add specification COLOR value (admin — válido ✅)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": {{specValueId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Add specification SIZE value (admin — válido ✅)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": 2
}

### ==========================================

### Add specification TEXT value (admin — válido ✅)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": 3
}

### ==========================================

### Add spec val (editor — válido ✅)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": {{specValueId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Add spec val (customer — 403 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": {{specValueId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Add spec val (sin token — 401 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": {{variantId}},
    "specification_value_id": {{specValueId}}
}

### ==========================================

### Add spec val (variant no existe — 404 ❌)
POST {{baseUrl}}/variant/spec-val HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "variant_id": 999,
    "specification_value_id": {{specValueId}}
}


### ==========================================
### VARIANT — ACTIVATE / DEACTIVATE (admin + editor)
### ==========================================

### Activate variant (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate variant (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate variant (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/activate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Activate variant (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/activate HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Deactivate variant (admin — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate variant (editor — válido ✅)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate variant (customer — 403 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Deactivate variant (sin token — 401 ❌)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}}/deactivate HTTP/1.1


### ==========================================
### VARIANT — DELETE (solo admin)
### ==========================================

### Delete variant (admin — válido ✅)
### Trigger elimina fotos automáticamente
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ==========================================

### Delete variant (editor — 403 ❌ solo admin puede eliminar)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{editorToken}}

### ==========================================

### Delete variant (customer — 403 ❌)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{customerToken}}

### ==========================================

### Delete variant (sin token — 401 ❌)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/variant/{{variantId}} HTTP/1.1

### ==========================================

### Delete variant (no existe — 404 ❌)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/variant/999 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


